g.text: GET /: renders default form otherwise Not Found XX
GET /{id}/{path}: renders form {id} in a specific path
POST /{id}/{path}: handles posted form {id} in a specific path
-- Preview Mode routes (when the user sets the runner to Preview Mode)
POST /publish: publishes a form JSON payload
GET /published/{id}: servers a form {id} JSON payload
GET /published: servers a list with all published forms' JSON payloads
